library(BiocBuildFailureDiagnosis)
dat <- explainBiocBuildFailure(package = "Rhisat2",
                               biocVersion = BiocManager::version(),
                               buildNodes = c("nebbiolo2", "tokay2", 
                                              "machv2", "nebbiolo1",
                                              "riesling1", "palomino3",
                                              "merida1"),
                               showOnlyFailing = FALSE,
                               repo = "BioCsoft",
                               dependencies = c("Depends", "Imports"))
